Author: AndrewJosten
Text: I was trying to buy prepaid electricity at the same time and the store clerk printed the slip before confirming my address and when I asked if I could just double check my address she kinda lost it at me.  Update tho, the boyfriend could see how much I wanted that sugar, so he ventured out afterwards to go buy me something and he curled up in my lap while I ate it. He can be a pain but he's also the best <3
